subproject.corporate outcome: Development plans and programmes integrate environmentally sustainable solutions in a manner that promotes poverty reduction, MDG achievement and low-emission climate-resilient development
subproject.description: TPMP is aimed at phasing out the consumption of the remainingCFCs (Cholo fluoro carbons) in The Gambia by 2010 and sustaining the phase out process of CFCs and other ODS.
subproject.title: TPMP GAMBIA GAM/PHA/53/INV/18
